==Introduction==
The '''Instance Actions''' is a component of a [[Help:Navigator|Navigator]] widget.

It displays buttons with actions which can be performed on the data entity instance displayed on the current page.

The following buttons are made available (subject of various conditions):
* [[Image:Concept Add Icon.png|20px]] '''Add {Aggregated Concept Name}''', for every Concept which is a part (aggregation) of the current entity. See [[Help:Aggregation|Aggregation]] and [[Help:Composition|Composition]] for more details.


==Definition==
No configuration available. Widget is displayed automatically in a fixed location.


